OL,3,C'They said I was a danger': LGBTQ+
OL,4,Cveterans speak out 25 years after 'gay
OL,5,Cban'
OL,7,FTwenty-five years after the Armed
OL,8,FForces so-called 'gay ban' was lifted,
OL,9,FBritish LGBTQ+ military veterans have
OL,10,Fshared their experiences in a new
OL,11,Fcomic strip.
OL,13,FSteve Purves was dishonourably
OL,14,Fdischarged from the Air Force in 1985,
OL,15,Fwhen he was found to be in a
OL,16,Frelationship with a man.
OL,18,FCourt marshalled and dismissed with
OL,19,Fdisgrace, he lost all his financial
OL,20,Fbenefits and served six months in
OL,21,Fprison.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
