OL,3,C'They said I was a danger': LGBTQ+
OL,4,Cveterans speak out 25 years after 'gay
OL,5,Cban'
OL,7,F"I was so angry about it all because I
OL,8,Fdidn't feel it should be happening,"
OL,9,Fhe told ITV News. "I kept thinking
OL,10,Fsomeone would intervene and quash it,
OL,11,Fbut they never did.
OL,13,F"It took a long time to come to terms
OL,14,Fwith what had happened and to face it.
OL,15,FYears and years and years and years
OL,16,Ffor me."
OL,18,FNow, Steve's story, among other LGBTQ+
OL,19,Fveterans', is being told in a new
OL,20,Fanthology comic, Coming Home, from
OL,21,Fcharity Re-Live.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
