OL,3,C'They said I was a danger': LGBTQ+
OL,4,Cveterans speak out 25 years after 'gay
OL,5,Cban'
OL,7,FThis month's edition focuses on the
OL,8,Fenduring impact of the UK military's
OL,9,F'gay ban' on veterans' mental health,
OL,10,Fmarking the 25th anniversary of the
OL,11,Flifting of the ban.
OL,13,FUntil 2000, homosexuality was banned
OL,14,Fin the Armed Forces. Under the ban,
OL,15,Fthousands of LGBTQ+ service personnel
OL,16,Fwere subjected to surveillance and
OL,17,Finterrogation and faced court
OL,18,Fmartials, dismissals for conduct
OL,19,Funbecoming and even imprisonment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
