OL,7,FIt wasn't until July 2023 that the
OL,8,Fthen Prime Minister Rishi Sunak
OL,9,Fapologised to the hundreds of veterans
OL,10,Fwho were persecuted.
OL,12,FThe stories in Coming Home are co-
OL,13,Fcreated with each veteran and a
OL,14,Fprofessional cartoonist to develop
OL,15,Ftheir own narrative.
OL,17,FSteve describes the process of making
OL,18,Fthe comic as thrilling and says the
OL,19,Ffinished product helps him to tell
OL,20,Fothers about his experience.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
