OL,7,F"You don't have to explain, warts and
OL,8,Fall, what happened to you. You say,
OL,9,Fokay, well, have a read. I'm the third
OL,10,Fstory in there, have a quick read and
OL,11,Fthen you'll know where I'm coming from
OL,12,Fand what I'm about."
OL,14,FLieutenant Caroline Paige worked with
OL,15,Fartist Ria Grix to depict her story.
OL,16,FCaroline knew she was transgender from
OL,17,Fa young age, but had to hide who she
OL,18,Fwas to serve in the Air Force.
