OL,3,C'They said I was a danger': LGBTQ+
OL,4,Cveterans speak out 25 years after 'gay
OL,5,Cban'
OL,7,FAfter years of service, Caroline
OL,8,Fdecided to leave the Air Force,
OL,9,Fknowing they would likely throw her
OL,10,Fout.
OL,12,F"I had this brilliant job, but I was
OL,13,Fmissing my life and I needed to do
OL,14,Fsomething about it," she said.
OL,16,FWith support from a medical officer,
OL,17,FCaroline was eventually allowed to
OL,18,Fstay in the service and transition.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
