OL,3,C'They said I was a danger': LGBTQ+
OL,4,Cveterans speak out 25 years after 'gay
OL,5,Cban'
OL,7,F"The ban was still in place and all of
OL,8,Fthe opinions were against me being in
OL,9,Fservice," Caroline said.
OL,11,F"They said I was a danger and a
OL,12,Fliability. It wasn't for a short while
OL,13,Funtil people started standing up for
OL,14,Fme and saying, hang on a minute,
OL,15,FCaroline's not the one who is the
OL,16,Fproblem, you are."
