OL,3,C'They said I was a danger': LGBTQ+
OL,4,Cveterans speak out 25 years after 'gay
OL,5,Cban'
OL,7,FThe veterans' stories resonate with
OL,8,FOlympian and former Army Sergeant Dame
OL,9,FKelly Holmes.
OL,11,FDespite being made an Honorary Army
OL,12,FColonel, she lived in fear of coming
OL,13,Fout for decades.
OL,15,FShe told ITV News: "I was in a career
OL,16,Fwhere it's illegal to be gay, I then
OL,17,Fleft that career where no one in
OL,18,Fsociety talked about, you know,
OL,19,Fsexuality as such. And in a sport
OL,20,Fwhere it was just a taboo subject, no
OL,21,Fone knew anything.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
