OL,7,FKarin Diamond, artistic director of Re-
OL,8,FLive, the charity behind the comic,
OL,9,Fsaid it was a "privilege" to "listen
OL,10,Fand be a witness to a veteran's story".
OL,12,F"At times it can be quite difficult to
OL,13,Fhear their experiences and know that
OL,14,Fthey've gone through such awful, awful
OL,15,Ftimes," she said.
